      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">22.202</ph> Contract clause.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d1308e8" class="- topic/p ">Insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1055332.dita#i1055332"
                  base="i1055332"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">52.222-3</xref>, Convict Labor,
in solicitations and contracts above the micro-purchase threshold,
when the contract will be performed in the United States, Puerto
Rico, the Northern Mariana Islands, American Samoa, Guam, or the
U.S. Virgin Islands; unless-</p>
         <ol id="d1278e22" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1308e15" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> The
contract will be subject to <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">41 U.S.C. chapter 65</xref>, <ph rev="FAC 2020-06 June 5, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-007?>(see<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 22.202 by removing from paragraph (a) “, Contracts for Materials, Supplies, Articles, and Equipment Exceeding $15,000”.?></ph>
                  <xref href="FAR-i1097464.dita#i1097464"
                        base="i1097464"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  22.6</xref>), which
contains a separate prohibition against the employment of convict
labor;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1308e30" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> The supplies
or services are to be purchased from Federal Prison Industries,
Inc. (see <xref href="FAR-i1117091.dita#i1117091"
                        base="i1117091"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  8.6</xref>); or</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1308e38" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> The acquisition
involves the purchase, from any State prison, of finished supplies
that may be secured in the open market or from existing stocks,
as distinguished from supplies requiring special fabrication.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
